data.value:
If you need help or have any questions, please send me an email to maud.picq@gmail.com
The status bar displays the current state of the tool: - "recording initial data" - "experimenting": during this phase, you will be able to see an estimate of the amount of time you wasted in the last 15 minutes in the task bar, on a color scale:
RED = wasting more than 75% of your time ORANGE = wasting between 50 and 75% of your time YELLOW = wasting between 25 and 50% of your time GREEN = wasting less than 25% of your time
- "analyzing data" - "report generated": the experiment is now finished; please click on the link to fill a quick survey, and then send the report (named Report_UserProductivity.txt, and located on your desktop) by email to maud.picq@gmail.com.
